Answer.comments: On one phrase, after I typed, the recordings did not continue for a minute or two.  I re-typed it, hit enter again, and after another time hitting enter, it finally went through.  I am hoping that all of my transcriptions were captures.
Answer.guess_accent: Somewhere in Asia, but not sure which country.
Answer.language_background_free: I am only fluent in English, but do know a little bit of German and Spanish.
